data.description: PRICE REDUCTION!!!!!! Are you looking for a large home to fit the whole family? Well, look no further! Welcome Home to this nicely built home on a cul-de-sac in the heart of Citrus County. This home offers a first-floor master with a large walk-in closet and an en suite with double sinks. Upstairs features 4 bedrooms,2 baths, a laundry room, and an additional living space, however it does need some TLC. This home is less than a mile from the Veterans Highway making traveling to Tampa quick and easy.
